text: "There's Nothing Holdin' Me Back" is a 2017 song by Canadian singer Shawn Mendes and is taken from his second studio album Illuminate (2016). It topped the single charts in Guatemala and Serbia. It went to the top 10 in Australia, Austria, Belgium, Brazil, Canada, Costa Rica, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Ecuador, Germany, Ireland, Israel, Malaysia, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Poland, Portugal, Slovakia, Slovenia, Switzerland, the United Kingdom, the United States and Venezuela.
